stories.description:
Auto width: Demonstrates the Range component with automatic width calculation.

Features:
- Automatic width calculation based on the parent container
- Smooth sliding interaction
- Proper value display

```tsx
<Range
  value={value}
  onChange={setValue}
  min={0}
  max={100}
  trackSize={{
    width: "auto",
    height: 6,
  }}
  thumbSize={12}
/>
```

